{
  "stem": "19111.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 119.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they kept digging a tunnel from that hole that they were held in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were successful to dig a 35, 40-foot tunnel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that tunnel ended right outside of the fence.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And at one point, they decided to-- to run away from there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so they were able to go through the tunnel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And 40 of them made it to the outside, at which point, the German guard noticed it and a mass hunt for them was-- was ensued.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they killed 25 right then and there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then 15 escaped. 11 made it to the partisans in the woods.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But what happened was after that, they needed more people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they came to Kailis.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they selected 70 men from Kailis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they took them there to continue this horrendous job as a replacement.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were just-- we were just there, languishing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got a little room where to sleep over for a few months.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, when the news spread that they're going to liquidate the Kaunas Ghetto, it was-- a panic had stricken all the people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People were trying to find-- they called it [NON-ENGLISH], which was a hiding places to hide.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were a lot of people who went into hiding.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father and-- has discovered a [INAUDIBLE] hiding place, where there were a lot of people going into.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he took us all in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But before anything happened, we had to get out of there because there was so little oxygen left, my father couldn't breathe.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was dying right then and there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we just walked out of there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in one of those buildings underground.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had a-- a place there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
